      "text": "- **|| (Logical OR):** Evaluates to true\nif **either** operand is true. code\nJavaScript",
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "- **|| (Logical OR):** Evaluates to true if **either** operand is true. code JavaScript",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "kg8YJ6DAllGchW8M2QaQu",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -1255.6944058755194,
      "y": 7758.9175782005605,
      "width": 791.99951171875,
      "height": 180,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#f38ba8",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
