      "text": "- **|| (Logical OR):** Evaluates to true\nif **either** operand is true. code\nJavaScript",
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "- **|| (Logical OR):** Evaluates to true if **either** operand is true. code JavaScript",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
