      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1780923104969,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "- **Short-Circuiting:** If the left-hand\noperand is true, the right-hand operand\nis **never evaluated**. This is commonly\nused to provide default values.",
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "- **Short-Circuiting:** If the left-hand operand is true, the right-hand operand is **never evaluated**. This is commonly used to provide default values.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
