      "text": "Don't memorize the entire precedence table. \nWhen in doubt, use parentheses () to make the order\nexplicit and your code more readable.",
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Don't memorize the entire precedence table. \nWhen in doubt, use parentheses () to make the order explicit and your code more readable.",
